reviews.text: Surprisingly good little wonton shop
In my opinion this is better than Mak's. V nice lady boss too. Good bowl of noodle with wholesome dumpling, my bestie had 2 full bowls at a go!

Very delicious
IMO, it's better than Mak's noodles
I like the Shrimp Wanton & Handmade Fishballs. Recommend the Wanton with chilli very tasty. The chilli oil can arouse your appetite in your mouth.
i extremely like the strimp wuton noodles offered by this shop. it's very special and tasty.  i hardly find similar taste . hope this shop would last longer!

reviews.text: 每次過來大角咀都會唸起呢間小店，傳統味道，湯頭正，其他食物中至上，保證放得落囗，價錢大衆化。
正正常常嘅一間雲吞店， 唔好諗住有咩驚喜
好食，又平云吞麵加菜再加汽水只收42元
好食！好好食！小店一間,坐位有限,招呼週到！
翠園地方清潔，老闆及老闆娘親切。
